TETRAPOL receiver

For lisensing see COPYING file.

set of tool which shloud allow its user
  - find TETRAPOL control channels and identify base stations
  - recieve TETRAPOL downlink transmissions
  - TODO: deltect and decode uplink transmission
  - TODO: decode recieved audio

features wich are not planned are:
  - Tx of signals
  - killing cats



Additional integration shipped in this repository:
  - native high-level streaming decoder API for external front-ends
  - SDRSharp / SDR# plugin sample in plugins/sdrsharp-tetrapol
